These files support the POSIX implementation of the producer-consumer project.

Source files:

- main.c (main program to simulate producer-consumer problem)

- buffer.c (implementation of buffer)

- buffer.h (header file containing function prototypes)

Makefile

To run the make file, enter "make"

To run the example program, enter "./example argv[1] argv[2], argv[3]"

argvs are all intergers!!!

argv[1] -----> sleep time of main program
argv[2] -----> number of producer
argv[3] -----> number of consumer
